{
  "stem": "27507.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And because, of course, we were officially permitted, somehow we managed to get into it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We got into the shop.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And that, I think, is probably the last I saw our flat in [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I don't think we ever went back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I think my parents probably managed to get some bits of furniture from there, and some things out of there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And we still-- the old sofa was still moving with us during that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "My mother somehow still managed to get a cart, or some kind of transport, to get that sofa into one of the places we moved on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But otherwise, I never went back there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I forgot to tell you about the bridge, but it doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And then we spent the next weeks, we spent very close in the shop, all the time in the shop, or shop I mean a factory.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "It was a factory building, or near to the factory building.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And we never dared to move, certainly not during those weeks after, to move far from there, because the weeks after-- the weeks, that means between the end of July 20th of July and something like the 7th, 8th of September, that was the so-called big action, where practically the whole of the ghetto was emptied, when people were taken, and brought to the [GERMAN], brought to the siding, taken from there in trains, and shipped to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 78
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "We didn't know what Treblinka was at this stage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And we didn't know that it existed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And we didn't know what was happening with the people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "But the fear was already absolutely immense.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
